## Impact Assessment

Unauthorized user accounts can provide attackers with persistent access to the system.

---

## Recommended Response

- Disable unauthorized accounts.
- Review administrator activity.
- Investigate related authentication events.
- Reset compromised credentials if necessary.

---

## Lessons Learned

Monitoring account creation events allows SOC analysts to detect persistence techniques before attackers establish long-term access.
